summary: Adds a few flowers at the front of Breezhome and some wheat and flowers in the back (accesible by gate)
descriptionHtml:
Version 2

**********************************************************************************

Version 2 this time this is more in line with the user\'s request:
http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/topic/647485-a-simple-breezhome-request/page__gopid__5105910#entry5105910

See Images for addons.

Installation just put the .esp in your data foler. Done!

Many Thanks,
Jedijas


**************************************************************

This mod is in response to this:

http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/topic/647485-a-simple-breezhome-request/page__gopid__5105381#entry5105381

Please read before you nag me with comments like:
\"Why is there a flower in my hat?\"
\"How did the gate kill me??!!!\"

thank you

Basically just does what the user requested adds a few flowers to the front of the house
and some flowers and wheat in the back of the house (accessible by gate).

Installation:
Just put the .esp in your data folder. Done!

Many thanks,
Jedijas
author: Jedijas
